# Google Drive only — copy names into Railway (values are examples).
# 1) Create a folder inside a Workspace *Shared drive* (not "My Drive").
# 2) Add the service account email from the JSON as a member of that shared drive.
# 3) Paste the folder id from the browser URL.

DRIVE_ONLY=1
GOOGLE_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID=1abcDEFghIJKlmnOPqRS_tuvwxyZ

# One of these (service account JSON from Google Cloud / Firebase):
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON=...  OR  GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON=...

# Personal @gmail.com: use OAuth instead of the two steps above; set:
# GOOGLE_DRIVE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_DRIVE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=
# GOOGLE_DRIVE_OAUTH_REFRESH_TOKEN=
# and remove DRIVE_ONLY if you also need Firestore/Sheets.
